---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About LLM Matcher — Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="About LLM Matcher and our affiliate partnership disclosure.">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:780px;padding-top:2rem">
    <h1>About LLM Matcher</h1>
    <p>LLM Matcher helps you find the best open-source AI models to run on your local hardware. We track GPU VRAM requirements, model performance, and provide ollama commands for instant setup.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top:2rem">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you click through and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the site free and up to date.</p>
    <p>Our current affiliate partners include:</p>
    <ul style="color:var(--text-secondary);padding-left:1.5rem;margin-top:.5rem;line-height:2">
      <li><strong>Amazon</strong> — GPU hardware recommendations</li>
      <li><strong>RunPod</strong> — Cloud GPU rental</li>
      <li><strong>Surfshark</strong> — VPN service</li>
      <li><strong>Pluralsight</strong> — AI/ML online courses</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem">We only recommend products and services we genuinely believe are useful to our readers.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top:2rem">Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions or partnership inquiries, reach us at the contact info in our GitHub repository.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
